00:25:27.185 --> 00:25:28.810 align:middle line:84%
Are we reproducing
goods with machines?

00:25:28.810 --> 00:25:31.440 align:middle line:84%
Are we producing
goods with labor?

00:25:31.440 --> 00:25:34.740 align:middle line:84%
What happens to the
