00:25:34.740 --> 00:25:36.720 align:middle line:90%
a decline in manufacturing?

00:25:36.720 --> 00:25:38.610 align:middle line:84%
It comes from
having more inputs.

00:25:38.610 --> 00:25:41.640 align:middle line:84%
So these are the kind of
ingredients, labor and capital

00:25:41.640 --> 00:25:46.320 align:middle line:84%
being kind of obvious labels
